{"tid":1999544,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★經濟新衝擊！有工人無訂單　內地恐爆裁員潮","createTime":"2020-05-03T09:02:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-03T13:56:38.000Z","uid":19454,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"fc1ad4f582b1618f0ad586ef37febc7a30ecf8be","tid":1999544,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T09:02:01.000Z","msg":"疫情繼續肆虐歐美等地，深圳鞋廠李老闆透露，有的買家3月、4月開始取消單，有的要求延後出貨，有的直接說訂貨不要了。他指，工廠沒有訂單就不會生產，周圍部分鞋廠更直接讓工人放假，5月及6月都不用上班。<br />\n<br />\n在鄭州經營3家手機零件工廠的羅老闆稱，他算是蘋果公司的下游廠商，3月訂單按年下滑至少7成，3月直接請還困在家鄉的工人不用回廠。<br />\n<br />\n在全球減單衝擊下，中國工廠為了生存紛以裁員、減薪、無薪假或不讓工人加班等方式應對。李老闆稱，不加班對農民工收入影響很大，每月基本收入可能只剩下兩千多元人民幣。在這種情況下很多人選擇離職。中國的農民工群體約有2.91億人。<br />\n<br />\n報道引述分析稱，中國經濟今年第一波衝擊來自中國的疫情，第二波來自海外訂單減少，第三波將是前兩波疫情造成企業倒閉、消費降低和大幅失業的惡性循環。瑞銀集團早前估計，中國正面臨20多年來最糟的就業市場，今年3月底，中國服務、製造和建築業中約有7,000萬至8,000萬人失去了工作或沒有上班工作。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20200503/bkn-20200503160909427-0503_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20200503%2Fbkn-20200503160909427-0503_00842_001.html&d=5G%2Bx0n%2BFJXS0hP%2BJIuhjgoE4T4y%2BYV5jPOnVoTo%2FPYs%3D&h=aeba388c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20200503/bkn-20200503160909427-0503_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"5960cece34b1b8d2b079e90274cd6577b24d7f9b","tid":1999544,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T09:02:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73e067602dd36a11c02d49bd7f90b18a5b448270","tid":1999544,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T09:08:12.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"a28448601fccb1fe88e441018af4ae4ca80a7aa4","tid":1999544,"uid":35930,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T09:09:41.000Z","msg":"老貓 支爆你驚唔驚自己冇糧出？"},{"pid":"beb48b6d816286585d7b319b61ad09ab2bc2d914","tid":1999544,"uid":121580,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a28448601fccb1fe88e441018af4ae4ca80a7aa4","tid":1999544,"uid":35930,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T09:09:41.000Z","msg":"老貓 支爆你驚唔驚自己冇糧出？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T09:12:49.000Z","msg":"佢無返工好耐LA<br />\n返工=不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38a451306379b99c18d83a374ce9f34b92628ca6","tid":1999544,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T13:52:25.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"29cdff613985dece43105dd5cc4f2e97079acf44","tid":1999544,"uid":179729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a28448601fccb1fe88e441018af4ae4ca80a7aa4","tid":1999544,"uid":35930,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T09:09:41.000Z","msg":"老貓 支爆你驚唔驚自己冇糧出？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T13:56:38.000Z","msg":"佢幾層樓收租都要返工？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}